   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-a" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Right. I still don't have an idea what kind of person he is.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Hmm... As I've told you before, I can vouch for him.<BR>But I guess you want more details than that, isn't it?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-b" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Then I'll give you more information about him.<BR>By right, I would ask for something in return, but I received something in advance so…….<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Fargeau keeps the catnip safely in his pocket.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-c" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Arc has been in Merca's Heart for a long time.<BR>He was one of the elves who managed the <FONT color=#086171>Distorted Zone</FONT> more than 200 years ago.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-d" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Are all elves here like that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>I don't know what happened but one day he suddenly left the other elves and joined the Anti-Goddess Faction.<BR>It is an exceptional case for an elf who is not even a resident of Merca to join the Anti-Goddess Faction. Elves never disobey the goddess.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-e" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Of course.<BR>They never leave the area they are assigned to, since they see it as their fate assigned by the goddess.<BR>There are rare cases that make them leave, like receiving special missions from the goddess.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-f" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So that's obeying the goddess too.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>For example, escorting the next Oracle-to-be to the Empire.<BR>For such missions, the elves will leave their assigned area to embark on a journey to the Empire as Holy Soldiers.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-g" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Could there be a special reason?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>That's right. So Arc seems unique and special to me.<BR>He seems more like a human than an elf. What could have made him like that…….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-g" image="QN_april.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Probably?<BR>I think it was pretty recent that he started talking about the Anti-Goddess Faction…<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Merchant</FONT><FONT color=#a82424> April</FONT> probably knows more about him than me.</html>]]></talk_question>
