   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-a" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Ask her about Arc.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Welcome. Is there anything you're looking for?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-b" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How did you know?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Oh the elf with a scar on one eye? Why ask about him all of a sudden?<BR>Oh, I think I know why. Did he approach you talking about the Anti-Goddess Faction too?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-c" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>He comes to buy stuff sometimes and bothers me with a lot of questions. Not only me but everyone else too.<BR>He pokes around asking strange questions and keeps wanting to meet Vernicka......</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-d" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Take someone?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>He's dark and suspicious. All elves are puppets of the goddess. I hope he doesn't harm anyone.<BR>Or is he trying to take someone again……?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-d" image="QN_Npc_Trader_Phara.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Oh you probably don't know about it.<BR>Long ago, the elves from <FONT color=#086171>Distorted Zone</FONT> took a <FONT color=#a82424>girl</FONT> to Holy Edart Empire.<BR>Oh, <FONT color=#a82424>Granny Sarrah</FONT> knows about it better than I do.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3" image="QN_Npc_Trader_Phara.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>That girl was her apprentice.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Granny Sarrah</FONT> can probably tell you more about it. Go and ask her.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-check_quest" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Explain what's going on.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>Hello child. You have lovely eyes.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-e" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>I see… So you want to know more about <FONT color=#a82424>Pitya</FONT>'s incident.<BR>So much time has passed but I remember it like it was yesterday.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-c" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>I never thought I would hear her name from another person.<BR>Especially from such a familiar-looking child…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-d" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>An Oracle candidate?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Pitya</FONT> was like a disciple to me.<BR>
She was a bright and kind-hearted girl.<BR>But one day, she was chosen as an <FONT color=#a82424>Oracle candidate</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-e" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>That's right. The High Priestess of <FONT color=#086171>Holy Edart Empire</FONT> and a vessel of Goddess Vestinel.<BR>But this story is too long so I'll tell you about it another time... For now, I'll tell you what you want to know first.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-f" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Was there an elf with a scar on one eye too?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>It was an ordinary day just like any other day…….<BR>I was tidying up the goods with her and the elves from <FONT color=#086171>Distorted Zone</FONT> suddenly appeared. They snatched her away like they were taking a prisoner. Both her fiance and I couldn't do anything.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-g" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Strangely?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>An elf with a scar......<BR>Oh, I think I remember him. It's hard to forget such a big scar.<BR>Come to think of it, that elf... Right, he acted rather strangely.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-h" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>Elves normally act as if they don't have emotions. They are puppets of the goddess who only follow her orders.<BR>However, that elf let go of Pitya's arm when she cried and tried to escape. And he seemed shocked and in pain.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-i" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>He seemed to have a sad history... He didn't know what to do for a while and quickly followed the other elves who took Pitya.<BR>He came back to Merca after that but he never comes this way. I have a feeling he is trying to avoid me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-3-j" mid="56" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, it was helpful.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>That's all I can tell you.<BR>Did I answer your question enough?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-3-j" image="QW_107.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1836_sarah-4" mid="58" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>…!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR>If you want more information about that elf, why don't you go to <FONT color=#a82424>Broken Goldstone Canyon</FONT>?<BR>I saw him heading that way several times. Maybe you can find some clues about him there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1836_sarah-4" image="QW_107.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sarrah$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Broken Goldstone Canyon</FONT> is a dangerous place so be careful.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-a" mid="61" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Take a closer look.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="60"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(There is a strange mark at the corner of the stone wall. There seems to be some sort of a spell since it is shining faintly.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-b" mid="63" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="62"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Upon a closer look, it wasn't just a strange mark but luminescent words.)</FONT><BR><FONT color=#086171>…I can't believe it. Who would resist becoming the Oracle?<BR>High Priestess is the vessel of the goddess, one with tremendous power who is closest to our creator.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-c" mid="65" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="64"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#086171>But that human girl who looked surprisingly just like </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Camellia</FONT><FONT color=#086171> was truly tormented.<BR>But why? Because she is a human who gets affected by emotions? Because she has a fiance she loves?<BR>Or is there a reason that I can't even fathom?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-d" mid="67" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="66"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Words disappear and new words appear in their place.)</FONT><BR><FONT color=#086171>…I've finished escorting the Oracle candidate.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#086171>My temporary job as a Holy Soldier ends here.<BR>But with the grace of the benevolent Goddess, I can stay in the outskirts of the empire for a few more days.</FONT> </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-e" mid="69" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="68"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#086171>Could it be because the Oracle candidate Pitya looked so much like her...?</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#086171>It's bothering me.<BR>I'm going to ask around for Camellia's news in the meanwhile.<BR>Even though she is a priestess who died long ago, there must be some records left.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-f" mid="71" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="70"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Words disappear and new words appear in their place.)</FONT><BR><FONT color=#086171>…I can't believe it. Did the Goddess really do this?<BR>Camellia… and many other women were used in </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>experiments</FONT><FONT color=#086171> and were killed in the process?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-g" mid="73" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="72"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#086171>She was much stronger and more beautiful than any other elf.<BR>She was someone chosen by the Goddess herself. She wasn't someone who could be sacrificed in experiments!<BR>Does the Goddess easily discard even those who are strong enough to win her favour…?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-h" mid="75" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="74"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#086171>Does Goddess Vestinel even have the slightest affection for her children?<BR>…I ...I thought Camellia would lead a happy and honourable life as a priestess after leaving me…</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-i" mid="77" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="76"><![CDATA[<html>$Strange Mark$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Words disappear and words in another colour appear this time.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2050_strange_trace-4-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-j" mid="79" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>?! (Wait a minute, how did he know?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="78"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc's Message$<BR>…This record only appears in reaction to energy from Lagendia.<BR>If it's not me who's reading this right now, it must be <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. </html>]]></talk_question>
