      <talk_answer link_index="n2050_strange_trace-4-l" mid="83" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(It's getting scary now...)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="82"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc's Message$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, I am not good with words and I don't have the talent to convince you. That is why I decided to show you part of the journal I recorded.<BR>If I do that, even if you ignore me right now, you would be concerned about what you read here and will find me one day.</html>]]></talk_question>
